sentences.english: France is one of the member states of the ELL.
sentences.chinese: 法国事欧罗巴洲同盟成员国之一。

sentences.english: King Agenor had a pretty daughter called Europa.
sentences.chinese: 国王阿革诺耳有一个美丽的女儿叫欧罗巴。

sentences.english: The Europa imitates a Buddha positive pain and sufferings but brave of face dashing billow.
sentences.chinese: 欧罗巴仿佛正痛苦但勇敢的面对着汹涌的巨浪。

sentences.english: Do the deposits on Europa also contain elemental sulfur?
sentences.chinese: 那么欧罗巴上的沉积物中也有单质硫吗？

sentences.english: Clotho took this skirt to Zeus and suggested Europa to him.
sentences.chinese: 克罗托把这件衣服要过来，让宙斯去送给欧罗巴。

sentences.english: The lanky Europe, cannot stop our Kingdom of Heaven's gold armored soldiers and iron horses.
sentences.chinese: 瘦瘦的欧罗巴，挡不住天朝的金戈铁马。

sentences.english: “European Gottlieb” means the place of the sun set, namely the west from which the name of Asia and Europe is transferred.
sentences.chinese: 亚细亚洲和欧罗巴洲的名称，就是由此转化而来。
